              "free_text": [
                " Array of eight large-volume NaI(Tl) detectors",
                "placed at roughly equally spaced angles from 40deg to",
                "160deg.Each NaI(Tl) detector core measures",
                "approximately 25.4 cm in diameter and 30.5 cm long.",
                "Surrounding the core detector is a segmented NaI(Tl)",
                "annular detector that is 7.5 cm thick and 30.5 cm",
